title: The Law of 100
itunes:title: The Law of 100
description:
Consistency is key! You don’t have to be smart to be successful, you don’t have to be sexy to be successful, you don’t even have to be good at most things to be successful! But one of the things that you need to be is consistent! In this episode, I’m gonna talk to you about the secret law of consistency that I called the law of 100.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
